item.description: Frauscher Sensortechnik GmbH FDS101 for FAdC/FAdCi v1.4.24 and all previous versions are vulnerable to a remote code execution (RCE) vulnerability via manipulated parameters of the web interface without authentication.Â This could lead to a full compromise of the FDS101 device.

item.title: CVE-2023-4152|2024-08-02T07:17:11.935Z -- frauscher -- fds101%20for%20fadc%2Ffadci
item.description: Frauscher Sensortechnik GmbH FDS101 for FAdC/FAdCi v1.4.24 and all previous versions are vulnerable to a path traversal vulnerability of the web interface by a crafted URL without authentication. This enables an remote attacker to read all files on the filesystem of the FDS101 device.
